{"word":"G1582 - ἐκκρέμαμαι - ekkrémamai - ek-krem'-am-ahee - Be very attentive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκκρέμαμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekkrémamai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-krem'-am-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be very attentive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செவிகொடு"},{"paragraph":"to hang from"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G2910 - κρεμάννυμι - kremánnymi - krem-an'-noo-mee/2910\">G2910</a>; to <i>hang upon</i> the lips of a speaker, that is, <i>listen closely:</i> - be very attentive.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1582/1582\">G1582</a>, <a href=\"#/G2910/2910\">G2910</a>"}]}